protected_spaces_details.description: Provision for children and young people

description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment of site to provide a part 7, part 11 storey mixed use building with basement parking to provide 291sqm of commercial space (A1/A2/A3/A4, B1(a), D1 Use Classes) together with 160 residential units with associated landscaping, children's play facilities and public riverside walkway.  (Alterations to the development approved under planning permission PA/13/03053 including a two-storey extension to Block A and a single-storey extension to Block B to provide 34 additional residential units and all associated works)
